# UI & terminal

## Aesthetic

- Near-black backgrounds (`#020202`, `#080808`), neutral borders, mono metrics
- Variant A: blue accents; Variant B: purple
- Match existing patterns; avoid generic “AI dashboard” redesigns

## App.tsx

- Landing overlay until `hasStarted`; then header nav + canvas + terminal
- `StreamingOverlay` uses `parsePartialJson` during generation
- Mobile: `mobileTab` + swipe between A/B; desktop: split view
- Keyboard: Enter/Space on focused variant to select
- `exportState` blocks interaction when set — use for export progress UI

## Terminal.tsx

- `parsePartialJson` for streaming fields; cache last valid `p5Code` to avoid flash
- `TerminalPanel`: metrics (time, TPS, tokens), Recharts `StatsChart`, code overlay
- JS download per variant when `data.p5Code` exists

## StatsChart

- Recharts only when container has non-zero size (ResizeObserver guard)

## UX copy

- “SELECT ON CANVAS” in selection mode; “EVOLVE” disabled during selection/generation
